Zero-Width Characters: Invisibly fingerprinting text: Manually retype to avoid invisible characters and homoglyphs. https://github.com/vedhavyas/zwfp

use a tool that strips non-whitelisted characters.

https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IDN_homograph_attack

General Punctuation: is a Unicode block containing punctuation, spacing, and formatting characters.
Range: U+2000..U+206F (112 code points)

space without width (invisible characters):
U+200B
U+200C
U+200D
U+FEFF
U+2060
U+2061
U+2062
U+2063
U+2064
U+206A
U+206B
U+206C
U+206E
U+206F

space with width:
U+2000
U+200A
U+202F
U+205F

https://www.irongeek.com/homoglyph-attack-generator.php

